  "texts": [
    "For SAAs, we observed higher accuracy overall and for each triage level when using representative vignettes.",
    "However, we also found a slightly lower safety of advice compared to the traditional set, whereas our findings regarding inclination to overtriage are inconclusive.",
    "When comparing different SAAs using the CCS, rankings varied significantly between traditional and representative vignettes.",
    "This highlights the crucial role of the vignette sets in SAA testing.",
    "When selecting an SAA for general use in guiding patients through the healthcare system, these different vignettes would lead to varying choices."
  ],
